              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-white hover:bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-4 py-3 border-r border-gray-100"><strong>Concrete Mold (Cetakan Beton)</strong></td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 border-r border-gray-100">Mencetak sampel uji beton. Tersedia bentuk Silinder (15x30 cm) dan Kubus (15x15x15 cm) bahan cast iron.</td>
